name: Gog & Magog
description: Gog & Magog, a strain produced by Israeli cannabis suppliers Tikun Olam, is an 80/20 indica-dominant hybrid. This variety is a top choice for patients seeking high-THC strains to treat conditions like nausea, inflammation, pain, and glaucoma. Gog & Magog are names referenced in the Qur'an and throughout the Bible.
attributes_title: Sleepy, Hungry, Uplifted, Euphoric, Happy, Insomnia, Lack of Appetite, Pain, Stress, Headaches, Dry Mouth, Dizzy
